author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Daimler: Jan Mercedes-Benz Brand Deliveries Up 8.4 Pct At 193,414 Vehicles
text:
Feb 6 (Reuters) - DAIMLER:
* SAYS MERCEDES-BENZ JAN DELIVERIES UP 5.9 PERCENT IN EUROPE, UP 16.4 PERCENT IN CHINA, DOWN 0.9 PERCENT IN USA
* SAYS JANUARY MERCEDES-BENZ BRAND DELIVERIES UP 8.4 PERCENT AT 193,414 VEHICLES
* SAYS JANUARY MERCEDES-BENZ CARS DELIVERIES UP 7.7 PCT AT 202,643 VEHICLES Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
